      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> coarsely</p>",
