    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, divide the<strong> cucumber & carrot salad</strong> between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>Thai-style coconut chicken</strong> – these are your<strong> zingy Thai-style coconut chicken wraps</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
